Future develops
***************

   Now the program works fine and is reliable, next version will be
optimized in memory usage.

   I intend to write the next version of Assigns in C++ and I'm
beginning to study some objects for programming in AmigaDOS.

   Lastly: make of Assigns an "Assign-Manager", but there are some
problems.


@EndNode

